        <updateDate>2021-06-01T14:41:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Support Peaceful Protest Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires an individual who is convicted of a federal offense related to the individual's conduct (e.g., rioting) during the course of a public gathering to pay the cost of federal policing activity during the public gathering. In addition, such an individual is ineligible for pandemic unemployment assistance.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
